*Teltoli cracks half a smile at the thought of having yet another group..*

"If there was another group, then I don't know what they'd stand for! We have the good.. the bad.. the neither.. and the ones who just sit around and destroy all three" *She laughs* "Although I do agree with your thought of Liono Prime. I, personally, have never met nor saw him.. but I have heard everyone elses thoughts of him"

*She sighs* "Sometimes I wish I hadn't joined the Maximals, that I had merely become Neutral.. but it wasn't to be!"

"So how long have you been on Earth?"
